As friends and family prepare to honour gospel star Lundi Tyamara with a memorial service this afternoon fellow musician Dr Malinga has dedicated a moving tribute to him and fellow gospel icon Sfiso Ncwane. Dr Malinga s musical tribute which he shared on social media is filled with a sense of sadness and a wave of emotion. Tribute to Lundi Tyamara and Sfiso Ncwane.A video posted by Dr Malinga (@drmalinga) on Jan 30, 2017 at 11:06pm PSTLundi died last Friday after a lengthy battle with stomach TB and liver complications. In the days that have followed Lundi s death his friends and family have remembered his strength and the contribution he s made to the music industry.A public memorial service will take place in honour of the gospel star at Grace Bible Church Soweto on Tuesday afternoon from 2pm.